OOC:Yeah, I am bringing in a new fraction...Joy...  Well here goes...


�Hedge�   �Sniper�   �Other Cybertron mob members�


   Scene open on a battleship called "Hedge's Revenge".  Camera zooms in 
over the Bridge from left to right.  You see sitting at a computer a red 
bot.  Standing behind this red bot is a short female bot looking over the 
red bot's shoulder.  In the middle seat, or as some might call it the 
command chair, is a character you might remember.  If you already guessed, 
it's Hedge.  Then sitting next to the right of Hedge, at the flight control 
is a bot with what looks like scales.  Suddenly the door opens and in walks 
a bulky bot.  He has a grey tent to him.

  "Sorry, I'm late." says Sniper (A character of mine from way back when.)

  "You are 5 minutes late, explain yourself."  Hedge says with a serious 
tone.

  "My alarm clock didn't work."  Sniper says.

  Hedge glares at Sniper, "That is no excuse."

  "I am sorry."  says Sniper.

  "Get to your command post and order Ostick and Thug-bot up here." Hedge 
says.

  "But they are on their break." Sniper snaps back.

  Hedge stands up and Slap's the stuffing out of Sniper's Mouth, "I said, 
Order than up here."

  "Yes ma'm." Sniper says as he goes to his command post.  He turns on his 
comm system.  "Will Ostick and Thug-bot please report to the bridge."
